DESCRIPTION:Lee &amp\; Hard Rock Cafe Presents The Ultimate Tribute to AC/D
 C &amp\; Guns N’ Roses ft. 2Blue YOU WILL LOVE HIM! ‘Cause he is not just a
  great singer! Tirthankar Poddar (aka 2Blue) is a muscular statement like a
  raised fist! With his four-octave militant-like voice and provocative stor
 ytelling\, he is known to dazzle. Small wonder when Paul Di`Anno of Iron Ma
 iden and George Lynch of Dokken came to India\, it was 2Blue they performed
  with. As did Bumblefoot of Guns N’ Roses. Come\, enrich your life. But be 
 warned. If you were born in the `80s and raised on vintage rock\, this coul
 d be emotional. Because chances are 2Blue is the artist you laughed and cri
 ed with when you were young. Chances are he is who you connected with on My
 Space and Orkut when you needed a friend. And over the years\, chances are 
 he is who you grew old with: the lead singer of Vayu who went solo\, the ma
 n who was crazy enough to quit his lucrative day job to headline your colle
 ge festival. Come\, enrich your life. Bring someone you love.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250127T062117Z
LOCATION:Hard Rock Cafe: Pune\, Amanora Mall\, Mundhwa - Kharadi Road\, Ama
 nora Park Town\, Hadapsar\, Pune\, Maharashtra 411028\, India
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Tribute to AC/DC & Guns N' Roses by 2Blue
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
