 ng-Join | Microsoft Teams</a><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><b
 r><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><b><b>Meeting Agenda: Security St
 rategy &amp\; Implementation Discussion</b></b><br><b><b>Date:</b></b> Tues
 day\, 7 April 2026<br><b><b>Time:</b></b> 10:30 AM<br><br><b><b>1. Opening 
 &amp\; Context Setting (5 mins)</b></b><ul><li>Overview of current security
  posture</li><li>Objectives of the meeting</li></ul><br><br><br><b><b>2. Cu
 rrent Security Operations (10 mins)</b></b><ul><li>Ongoing security practic
 es</li><li>Daily security alerts coordination</li><li>Status of security as
 sessments (applications)</li><li>Risk assessment updates</li></ul><br><br><
