 on status:<br>CMS<br>Yearheads <br>All APIs (pending)<br>• Discussion:<br>I
 dentity-based secret delivery (Secrets Manager)<br>Pull-based secret retrie
 val (Bitwarden)<br>• Decision on standardized approach<br><br><b><b>4. Secu
