  vs relying on platform security<br><br><b><b>6. Advanced Security Framewor
 ks (10 mins)</b></b><ul><li>Sentinel implementation discussion</li><li>Zero
  Trust Architecture (ZTA) approach and feasibility</li></ul><br><br><br><b>
 <b>7. Backup &amp\; Recovery Strategy (10 mins)</b></b><ul><li>Importance a
 nd applicability of the <u><u>3-2-1 backup rule at </u></u><b><b><u><u>curr
 ent infra stage</u></u></b></b></li><li>Recommendations and action plan</li
 ></ul><br><br><br><b><b>8. Code Security &amp\; Quality (10 mins)</b></b><u
 l><li>Final decision on SonarQube implementation</li><li>Integration approa
 ch and scope</li></ul><br><br><br><b><b>9. Open Discussion &amp\; Q&amp\;A 
 (5–10 mins)</b></b><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><p><br></p><br><
