 MO (25+ yrs) | Aligning with KEBA's Automation Mission\n\nHi Michael\,\n\nT
 his slot works best for me:\n\nTuesday\, December 2nd at 7:30 am (Vienna ti
 me) / 12:00 (IST)\n\nregards\n\nSandeep Jain\n\n\n\nOn Tue\, Nov 25\, 2025 
 at 3:41 PM bdr Broder Michael <bdr@keba.com<mailto:bdr@keba.com>> wrote:\nD
 ear Sandeep Jain\,\n\nI would like to come back to your offer. I am in char
 ge of Human Resources for KEBA Group and I would like to discuss possibilit
 ies regarding a cooperation.\nIf you are interested\, I can offer you the f
 ollowing options:\n\nTuesday\, December 2nd at 7:30 am (Vienna time) / 12:0
 0 (IST)\nFriday\, December 5th at 8 am / 12:30 (IST)\nFriday\, December 12t
