  you in advance\nMichael\n\n\nMichael Broder\n\nPeople\, Culture & Structur
 e\n\n\n\nKEBA Group AG\n\nReindlstraße 51\n\n4040 Linz/Austria\n\nPhone: +4
 3 732 7090-74224\n\nFax:     +43 732 7090-10\n\nMobile: +43 664 7867 1687\n
 \nCompany registration court: Linz FN 184376t\n\nbdr@keba.com<mailto:bdr@ke
