 15] <https://www.xing.com/pages/keba-group>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nVon: Sande
 ep Jain <jain111sandeep@gmail.com<mailto:jain111sandeep@gmail.com>>\nGesend
 et: Dienstag\, 9. September 2025 17:48\nAn: kle Kletzmaier Karl <kle@keba.c
 om<mailto:kle@keba.com>>\nBetreff: Subject: Leadership Interest – Delivery\
 , Governance & PMO (25+ yrs) | Aligning with KEBA's Automation Mission\n\n\
 n\nACHTUNG: Das Mail kommt von einer anderen Organisation ! Links nicht ank
 licken und Anhänge nicht öffnen\, außer der Absender ist bekannt und der In
 halt der Anlage ist sicher. Im Zweifelsfall bitte mit der Liste vertrauensw
 ürdiger Absender<https://collaboration.keba.com/trustedurls> gegenprüfen\, 
 oder  den KEBA IT-Servicedesk kontaktieren!\n\nCAUTION:  This email origina
 ted from outside of the organization. Do not click links or open attachment
 s unless you recognize the sender and know the content is safe. In case of 
 doubt please verify with the list of trustworthy senders<https://collaborat
 ion.keba.com/trustedurls>\, or contact the IT-Servicedesk!\n\nHello\,\n\nI'
 m writing to express my strong interest in a leadership role at KEBA\, spec
 ifically within Delivery\, Governance\, or PMO. While I couldn't find a dir
 ect HR contact\, I'd appreciate it if you could forward my inquiry to the r
 elevant hiring manager.\n\nI've been following KEBA's work and am impressed
  by your mission as a leader in industrial automation and robotics. Your fo
 cus on creating intelligent\, connected manufacturing solutions\, from HMI 
 and control systems to safety technology\, deeply resonates with my profess
 ional experience in technology transformation. My background in managing co
 mplex projects in high-growth tech environments is a strong match for your 
 forward-thinking approach.\n\nWith over 25 years of experience in the IT in
 dustry\, I've successfully built and led PMO frameworks\, delivery governan
 ce processes\, and remote-first teams for global organizations. My work spa
 ns large-scale transformation projects in sectors like Telecom and SaaS\, w
 here I've leveraged AI and cloud technologies to modernize operations and d
 rive strategic outcomes. This background gives me a unique perspective on m
 anaging complex technical projects in fast-paced\, high-growth environments
 \, including those that integrate hardware and software solutions.\n\n_____
 ___________________________\nHow My Experience Can Add Value to KEBA\n\n  *
    Strategic Delivery Management: I bring expertise in managing end-to-end 
 program execution for enterprise-grade solutions. My focus is on delivering
  customer-centric outcomes in high-tech domains. My experience in SaaS plat
 forms (AWS) is directly applicable to managing the delivery of sophisticate
 d software and cloud solutions that support complex hardware and industrial
  digitalization efforts.\n  *   Agile PMO Frameworks: I have a proven track
  record of building scalable governance structures across different regions
 . I can help establish the operational rigor needed for expansion while mai
 ntaining the agility essential for a global technology company.\n  *   Buil
 ding High-Performance Teams: I specialize in attracting\, hiring\, and deve
 loping top-tier talent. I can help build and lead high-performance\, collab
 orative global teams well-suited to the demands of a cutting-edge robotics 
 and automation company.\n\nMy experience in leading cross-regional teams an
 d building robust delivery frameworks from the ground up would be particula
 rly valuable as KEBA continues to scale its global operations and client ba
 se.\n\nYou can find more details about my background and skills here:\n\n  
 *   Portfolio: https://jainsandeep729.wixsite.com/website\n  *   LinkedIn: 
 https://www.linkedin.com/in/jain35/\n\nThank you for your time and consider
 ation. I am confident my experience in managing complex technical deliverie
 s and building strong teams aligns with KEBA's innovative mission. I look f
 orward to the possibility of connecting.\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSandeep Jain\n\n
